item.content:encoded:

Mouse or tap.

item.content:encoded:
Today is Natalia’s father’s birthday. Natalia’s father has to go out to work during the day. Five-year-old Natalia and her mother want to prepare for Father’s Day surprises for their father during this time. Natalia decides to wash his father’s car, and then cook his favorite steak for his father. Natalia’s mother will make a birthday cake. They need to go out to buy some ingredients and tools for car washing, buy birthday gifts for dad by the way, and give gifts to dad at night.
Mouse click or tap to play.

item.content:encoded:
Monster Nail Doctor is a delicate doctor-themed game. Each one of these four creepy creatures has really been neglecting themselves lately. They could definitely use some monstrous manicures. Can you fix up their feet in this game for girls? Help them go from ghoulish to gorgeous! If you are a doctor-themed game lover, what are you waiting for? Come and experience this game, if you like it, don’t forget to share it with your friends.
Click to control.
